      <title>瑞银希望在合并后的绿色改革中保留并增加航运贷款</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/sustainability/sustainable-finance-reporting/ubs-looks-keep-grow-shipping-loans-post-merger-green-overhaul-2024-03-28/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[瑞银高管告诉路透社，瑞银将寻求增加对航运业的贷款，并停止向瑞士信贷继承的化石燃料客户提供部分贷款，这是迄今为止大型合并对银行可持续发展承诺影响的最大考验。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/sustainability/sustainable-finance-reporting/ubs-looks-keep-grow-shipping-loans-post-merger-green-overhaul-2024-03-28/</guid>
